<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA29">
<l>uṇara voruvark keḷiyaṉē cevvē</l>
<l>yiṇarun tuḻāyalaṅka lentai yuṇarat</l>
<l>taṉakkeḷiya revvaḷava ravvaḷava rāṉā</l>
<l>leṉakkeḷiya ṉemperumā ṉiṅku.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is he easy to perceive for [any]one? When one directly</l>
<l>perceives our father on whom sways Tulsi in clusters,</l>
<l>however many they are, they are easy [to perceive] for him. Therefore,</l>
<l>our great lord here is easy [to perceive] for me.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
